snippet.title: Scream Go Hero: Eighth Note Yasuhati (Ketchapp)
snippet.description:
Play iOS ➡ https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/scream-hero/id1212039074?at=11lGxL&ct=youtube-screamhero

Play Android ➡ https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ketchapp.screamhero

Use your voice to move and jump between platforms. Soft voice to jump, scream to jump. Watch out!

Don't disturb your neighbour!
